document_data.mainbody: AnndoquatAnndoquats name is spelled Andoquat on the back cover of The Great Khan Game, but is spelled as Anndoquat on his game card.  was a sardar from the city of Al-Ubaid in the Whamite Isles. There, he had a group of personal bodyguards. Anndoquat represented Al-Ubaid in a series of wild conflicts between various nations and pirates of the Whamite Isles
